  <brief_title>OPERA: French Observational Study on Patients Implanted With a Guidant PRIZM or Vitality Defibrillator</brief_title>
  <official_title>OPERA: French Observational Study on Patients Implanted With a Guidant PRIZM or Vitality Defibrillator</official_title>
